01:11:41.400 --> 01:11:43.700
You are a darling.

01:11:43.700 --> 01:11:46.900
Penny,you were a brave little girl
to do what you did all by yourself.

01:11:46.900 --> 01:11:49.700
Oh, I didn't do it
all by myself.

01:11:49.600 --> 01:11:54.000
Two little mice from
the Rescue Aid Society helped me.

01:11:53.900 --> 01:11:57.200
Mice? Rescue Aid Society?

01:11:57.100 --> 01:11:59.500
Yes, they rescued me.

01:11:59.500 --> 01:12:02.900
Uh, could I say hello to them?
Hello, Bianca.!

01:12:02.900 --> 01:12:04.500
Hi, Bernard.!

01:12:04.400 --> 01:12:06.700
You can talk to these little mice?

01:12:06.600 --> 01:12:09.300
All the time.
Mice can talk like anybody.

01:12:09.200 --> 01:12:11.200
Didn't you know that?

01:12:11.100 --> 01:12:14.700
Well, uh, I didn't,
but I do now, Penny.

01:12:22.300 --> 01:12:26.100
Evinrude, what are you doing here?

01:12:31.400 --> 01:12:33.700
It's another call for help.

01:12:33.600 --> 01:12:35.700
Here, uh, uh...

01:12:35.700 --> 01:12:38.200
you're gonna need some volunteers.

01:12:38.100 --> 01:12:40.700
But-- B-But, B-Bianca,
we just--

01:12:40.700 --> 01:12:44.000
Oh, Bernard, adventure, thrills...

01:12:43.900 --> 01:12:46.900
intrigue, travel, exotic places.

01:12:46.900 --> 01:12:49.200
Oh, come on, darling. Let's go.

